🎯 **What:**
Extract the duplicated pattern `JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(filePath, "utf-8"))` into a centralized utility function `readJsonFileSync` inside `src/lib/core/file-utils.ts`.

💡 **Why:**
This improves the maintainability and readability of the codebase by replacing repeated one-liners across multiple files with a single, clear abstraction.

✅ **Verification:**
I created a unit test `src/lib/core/file-utils.test.ts` for the new utility. I ran `npm run test` on the changed files and `npm run verify:core` over the codebase to ensure nothing was broken. No functionality was altered.

✨ **Result:**
A cleaner codebase with centralized logic for JSON file reads.

